comments.text:
API endpoints now available (from giftlist-0mj.3):

- GET /api/notifications?cursor=X&limit=20 → { data: NotificationResponse[], pagination: { hasNext, nextCursor } }
- GET /api/notifications/unread-count → { count: number }
- POST /api/notifications/mark-read with { id } → NotificationResponse
- POST /api/notifications/mark-all-read → { count }
- DELETE /api/notifications/[id] → 204

NotificationResponse type: { id, userId, type, title, body, data, read, createdAt, updatedAt }

Files at: src/pages/api/notifications/

Notification integration is ready in src/lib/notifications.ts. When implementing invitation endpoints:

1. POST create invitation - use sendInvitationEmail():
   await notificationService.sendInvitationEmail({
     userId: existingUser?.id,  // optional - if invitee has account
     inviteeEmail, inviterName, groupName, inviteUrl,
     data: { groupId, invitationId }
   });

2. POST accept invitation - use notifyInvitationAccepted() + notifyMemberJoined():
   await notificationService.notifyInvitationAccepted({
     inviterId, accepterName, groupName, groupId
   });
   await notificationService.notifyMemberJoined({
     memberUserIds: existingMemberIds,
     newMemberName, groupName, groupId
   });

3. DELETE member (leave group) - use notifyMemberLeft():
   await notificationService.notifyMemberLeft({
     memberUserIds: remainingMemberIds,
     leftMemberName, groupName, groupId
   });
